{
  "video_id": "gmn7tjSNyAA",
  "title": "How to grow fresh air | Kamal Meattle",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12160.0,
      "end_time": 17160.0,
      "text": "Some 17 years ago, I became allergic to Delhi&#39;s air."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17160.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "My doctors told me that my lung capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20160.0,
      "end_time": 22160.0,
      "text": "had gone down to 70 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22160.0,
      "end_time": 23160.0,
      "text": "and it was killing me."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23160.0,
      "end_time": 26160.0,
      "text": "With the help of IIT,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26160.0,
      "end_time": 28160.0,
      "text": "TERI, and learnings from NASA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28160.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "we discovered that there are three"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31160.0,
      "end_time": 33160.0,
      "text": "basic green plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 33160.0,
      "end_time": 35160.0,
      "text": "common green plants, with which"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35160.0,
      "end_time": 36160.0,
      "text": "we can grow all the fresh air"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 36160.0,
      "end_time": 39160.0,
      "text": "we need indoors to keep us healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 41160.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve also found that you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 41160.0,
      "end_time": 43160.0,
      "text": "reduce the fresh air requirements"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 43160.0,
      "end_time": 45160.0,
      "text": "into the building, while maintaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 45160.0,
      "end_time": 48160.0,
      "text": "industry indoor air-quality standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48160.0,
      "end_time": 50160.0,
      "text": "The three plants are Areca palm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50160.0,
      "end_time": 54160.0,
      "text": "Mother-in-Law&#39;s Tongue and money plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 54160.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "The botanical names are in front of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58160.0,
      "end_time": 60160.0,
      "text": "Areca palm is a plant which"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 60160.0,
      "end_time": 64160.0,
      "text": "removes CO2 and converts it into oxygen."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 64160.0,
      "end_time": 68160.0,
      "text": "We need four shoulder-high plants per person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68160.0,
      "end_time": 70160.0,
      "text": "and in terms of plant care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 70160.0,
      "end_time": 71160.0,
      "text": "we need to wipe the leaves"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71160.0,
      "end_time": 73160.0,
      "text": "every day in Delhi, and perhaps"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73160.0,
      "end_time": 75160.0,
      "text": "once a week in cleaner-air cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75160.0,
      "end_time": 78160.0,
      "text": "We had to grow them in vermi manure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78160.0,
      "end_time": 81160.0,
      "text": "which is sterile, or hydroponics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81160.0,
      "end_time": 85160.0,
      "text": "and take them outdoors every three to four months."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 85160.0,
      "end_time": 88160.0,
      "text": "The second plant is Mother-in-law&#39;s Tongue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 88160.0,
      "end_time": 90160.0,
      "text": "which is again a very common plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 90160.0,
      "end_time": 92160.0,
      "text": "and we call it a bedroom plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 92160.0,
      "end_time": 95160.0,
      "text": "because it converts CO2 into oxygen at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95160.0,
      "end_time": 100160.0,
      "text": "And we need six to eight waist-high plants per person."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 100160.0,
      "end_time": 102160.0,
      "text": "The third plant is money plant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 102160.0,
      "end_time": 105160.0,
      "text": "and this is again a very common plant;"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 105160.0,
      "end_time": 108160.0,
      "text": "preferably grows in hydroponics."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 108160.0,
      "end_time": 111160.0,
      "text": "And this particular plant removes formaldehydes"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111160.0,
      "end_time": 112160.0,
      "text": "and other volatile chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 112160.0,
      "end_time": 114160.0,
      "text": "With these three plants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114160.0,
      "end_time": 116160.0,
      "text": "you can grow all the fresh air you need."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 116160.0,
      "end_time": 118160.0,
      "text": "In fact, you could be in a bottle"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 118160.0,
      "end_time": 122160.0,
      "text": "with a cap on top, and you would not die at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 122160.0,
      "end_time": 125160.0,
      "text": "and you would not need any fresh air."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 125160.0,
      "end_time": 127160.0,
      "text": "We have tried these plants at our"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 127160.0,
      "end_time": 130160.0,
      "text": "own building in Delhi, which is a"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130160.0,
      "end_time": 133160.0,
      "text": "50,000-square-feet, 20-year-old building."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133160.0,
      "end_time": 137160.0,
      "text": "And it has close to 1,200 such plants for 300 occupants."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 137160.0,
      "end_time": 139160.0,
      "text": "Our studies have found that there is"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 139160.0,
      "end_time": 143160.0,
      "text": "a 42 percent probability of one&#39;s blood oxygen"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143160.0,
      "end_time": 145160.0,
      "text": "going up by one percent if one stays indoors"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 145160.0,
      "end_time": 148160.0,
      "text": "in this building for 10 hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 148160.0,
      "end_time": 151160.0,
      "text": "The government of India has discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151160.0,
      "end_time": 153160.0,
      "text": "or published a study to show"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153160.0,
      "end_time": 156160.0,
      "text": "that this is the healthiest building in New Delhi."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156160.0,
      "end_time": 159160.0,
      "text": "And the study showed that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 159160.0,
      "end_time": 160160.0,
      "text": "compared to other buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160160.0,
      "end_time": 162160.0,
      "text": "there is a reduced incidence of"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 162160.0,
      "end_time": 164160.0,
      "text": "eye irritation by 52 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 164160.0,
      "end_time": 168160.0,
      "text": "respiratory systems by 34 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 169160.0,
      "text": "headaches by 24 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 169160.0,
      "end_time": 173160.0,
      "text": "lung impairment by 12 percent and asthma by nine percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 173160.0,
      "end_time": 177160.0,
      "text": "And this study has been published on September 8, 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 177160.0,
      "end_time": 180160.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s available on the government of India website."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 180160.0,
      "end_time": 182160.0,
      "text": "Our experience points to an"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 182160.0,
      "end_time": 186160.0,
      "text": "amazing increase in human productivity"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 186160.0,
      "end_time": 189160.0,
      "text": "by over 20 percent by using these plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189160.0,
      "end_time": 193160.0,
      "text": "And also a reduction in energy requirements in buildings"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 193160.0,
      "end_time": 199160.0,
      "text": "by an outstanding 15 percent, because you need less fresh air."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199160.0,
      "end_time": 200160.0,
      "text": "We are now replicating this in a"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 200160.0,
      "end_time": 203160.0,
      "text": "1.75-million-square-feet building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 203160.0,
      "end_time": 205160.0,
      "text": "which will have 60,000 indoor plants."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 205160.0,
      "end_time": 207160.0,
      "text": "Why is this important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 207160.0,
      "end_time": 209160.0,
      "text": "It is also important for the environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 209160.0,
      "end_time": 210160.0,
      "text": "because the world&#39;s energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 210160.0,
      "end_time": 212160.0,
      "text": "requirements are expected to grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212160.0,
      "end_time": 214160.0,
      "text": "by 30 percent in the next decade."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 214160.0,
      "end_time": 215160.0,
      "text": "40 percent of the world&#39;s energy is taken"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 215160.0,
      "end_time": 217160.0,
      "text": "up by buildings currently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 219160.0,
      "text": "and 60 percent of the world&#39;s population"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219160.0,
      "end_time": 222160.0,
      "text": "will be living in buildings in cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 222160.0,
      "end_time": 226160.0,
      "text": "with a population of over one million in the next 15 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228160.0,
      "text": "And there is a growing preference for living"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 228160.0,
      "end_time": 232160.0,
      "text": "and working in air-conditioned places."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 232160.0,
      "end_time": 234160.0,
      "text": "\"Be the change you want to see in the world,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 234160.0,
      "end_time": 235160.0,
      "text": "said Mahatma Gandhi."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 235160.0,
      "end_time": 236160.0,
      "text": "And thank you for listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 236160.0,
      "end_time": 238160.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}